NA AND RELATED ANTENNA ARRAY\n\n(71) Applicant: City University of Hong Kong, Kowloon (HK)\n\n(57) ABSTRACT\n\n(72) Inventors: Kwai Man Luk, Kowloon (HK); Jingtao Zeng, RongGui (CN)\n\nA planar complementary antenna and an antenna array with multiple planar complementary antennas. The planar complementary antenna has a substrate, a planar dipole antenna arranged on the substrate, a loop antenna arranged on the substrate and operably connected with the planar dipole antenna, and a feed network for connection with a feed source. The feed network is operably connected with the planar dipole antenna and the loop antenna for feeding an electrical signal from the feed source to the planar dipole antenna and the loop antenna so as to form an electric dipole at the planar dipole antenna and a magnetic dipole at the antenna.\n\n(21) Appl. No.: 16/502,131\n\n(22) Filed: Jul. 3, 2019\n\nPublication Classification\n\n(51) Int. CL.\n\nHO1Q 21/06 (2006.01) \u4e94 01O 7/00 (2006.01) HOIQ 138 (2006.01)\n\nL 903\n\nBottom layer\n\nloop\n\nPatent Application Publication\n\nJan. 7 , 2021 Sheet 1 of 14\n\nUS 2021/0005980 A1\n\n110\n\n103\n\nK108\n\n108C\n\n106\n\n108A2\n\n106D 116\n\nXE\n\n106C\n\nFigure 1C\n\nBottom\n\nlayer\n\n118\n\n108D\n\n108E\n\n100\n\n108A1\n\n106A\n\n106B 114 108A1\n\n108B\n\nFigure 1A\n\n104\n\n102\n\n102\n\n112B\n\n116\n\n120\n\n0-118\n\n103\n\nFigure 1B\n\nlayer\n\nTop\n\n114 112A\n\n112\n\nUS 2021/0005980 Al\n\nJan. 7,2021 Sheet 1 of 14\n\nPatent Application Publication\n\ncot \u4e4b YVIoInStH rade] doy. y \u20acor\n\noot \u4e4b\n\nOt ern3rUT\n\nqt arn3I\n\nPatent Application Publication\n\nJan. 7 , 2021 Sheet 2 of 14\n\nUS 2021/0005980 A1\n\n( 18p ) uleb\n\n2\n\nFrequency ( GHZ ) Figure 2\n\nl\u00f8p ) juapuaco uoppala\n\nJan. 7, 2021 Sheet 2 of 14\n\nUS 2021/0005980 Al\n\nPatent Application Publication\n\n(gp) ued\n\nsand Frequency (GHz) bea \u4e86\n\nae\n\nt\n\nAB\n\na\n\nFigure 2\n\naN z\n\noo (aphuarsyjeoo uonoayeny\n\nPatent Application Publication\n\